title: Top UK women’s groups ban transgender members
description: UK’s Girlguiding and the Women’s Institute ban transgender members after top court ruling on biological sex Read Full Article at RT.com
content:
Two of Britain’s biggest organizations for women and girls, Girlguiding and the Women’s Institute, have said they will no longer accept transgender members, citing a court ruling on biological sex.
